---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
			description="Raghavan Muthuregunathan builds search, retrieval, evaluation, and AI product systems that hold up in production."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="page">
			<section class="content">
				<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
				<h1>I like the layer where papers, logs, and user behavior all have to agree.</h1>
				<p>
					I am Raghavan Muthuregunathan, an engineering leader working at the intersection of
					search, information retrieval, machine learning, and applied AI systems. My work has
					focused on turning ambiguous user intent into useful product experiences: typeahead,
					spell correction, ranking, personalization, retrieval-augmented generation, assistants,
					and search systems that have to operate at real-world scale.
				</p>
				<p>
					I currently lead Search AI work at LinkedIn. Earlier in my career, I worked on Microsoft
					Bing, where I built experience in large-scale search infrastructure and relevance. That
					combination shaped how I approach new systems: start with the research, establish the
					baseline, build the evaluation harness, and keep pushing until the experience is reliable
					enough for people to use.
				</p>
				<p>
					I am especially interested in retrieval quality, multilingual and translation-augmented
					generation, trustworthy assistants, and the engineering discipline required to move from
					a promising model behavior to a customer-facing workflow.
				</p>
				<div class="about-list">
					<h2>Operating range</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Deep search and information retrieval experience across Bing and LinkedIn.</li>
						<li>Hands-on applied AI work across ranking, personalization, RAG, and assistant systems.</li>
						<li>Engineering leadership for teams shipping production experiences with measurable quality.</li>
						<li>
							Community work with open and public-interest AI efforts, including GenAI Commons,
							Apache Solr, and disaster-management AI initiatives.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<p>
					This site is my home base for experiments, writing, and projects around search, retrieval,
					evaluation, and applied intelligence. You can find my code and experiments on
					<a href="https://github.com/Raghavan1988">GitHub</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
